ABOUT US



A WORLD LEADER IN TESTING, INSPECTION & CERTIFICATION SERVICES

Founded in 1828, Bureau Veritas is a global leader in Testing, Inspection and Certification (TIC), delivering high quality services to help clients meet the growing challenges of quality, safety, environmental protection, and social responsibility. Bureau Veritas offers innovative solutions that go beyond simple compliance with regulations and standards, reducing risk, improving performance and promoting sustainable development.

 






  
  




 
 










 
 










 
 



















